layout.house_prompt: A modern living room featuring four sofa chairs surrounding a circular ceramic table, with two floor lamps positioned adjacent to the table. All the furniture is set on a large rectangular rug in the middle of the room. A large wooden tray with two glass bowls rests on top of the table. A mirror is mounted on the wall next to the window, flanked by a wall lamp on each side.
